    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it shows in every little detail. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for a new home, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
